Umurenge wa Muganza uhererereye mu majyepfo yuburengerazuba bw' akarere ka Rusizi (-2.6133136549023903, 29.01959164694231)<ref>https://www.google.com/maps/search/muganza+sector,+cimerwa/@-2.616829,28.9766763,13z</ref>.Ugizwe n'utugali dutatu aritwo Cyarukara, Gakoni na Shara<ref>https://rusizi.gov.rw/index.php?id=156</ref>; imwe mu mirenge bihana imbibi Bugarama, Rwimbogo, Gitambi na Gikundamvura. Uyu murenge niwo uherereyemo uruganda rwa CIMERWA ltd rukora isima<ref>https://cimerwa.rw/#</ref>, ukaba unazwiho guhinga umuceri dore ko ufite ubuso bunini bw'ikibaya. Bikaba byumvikana ko abaturage baho batuzwe cyane n'ubuhinzi.
